---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy | BingoPlace Limited"
  description="Privacy Policy and Data Protection statement for BINGOPLACE LIMITED, Manchester, UK."
>
  <section class="relative py-32 overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background Accents to match Home -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 bg-[#050A1A]">
      <div class="absolute top-[-10%] right-[-10%] w-96 h-96 bg-[#D4AF37]/5 blur-3xl rounded-full"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-white text-5xl md:text-6xl font-serif mb-6 leading-tight">Privacy <span class="text-[#D4AF37] italic">Policy.</span></h1>
        <p class="text-[#D4AF37] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[10px] font-bold mb-16">Effective Date: May 20, 2026</p>

        <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-12 text-slate-400 leading-relaxed font-light">
          
          <!-- Section 1 -->
          <section class="space-y-4">
            <h2 class="text-white text-2xl font-serif">1. Introduction</h2>
            <p>
              BINGOPLACE LIMITED ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting the privacy and security of your personal data. This policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you visit <strong>bingoplaceltd.com</strong> or engage with our wholesale services.
            </p>
            <p>
              As a UK-registered company (Company No: 16998502), we act as the "Data Controller" for the personal information you provide to us under the UK General Data Protection Regulation (UK GDPR).
            </p>
          </section>

          <!-- Section 2 -->
          <section class="space-y-4">
            <h2 class="text-white text-2xl font-serif">2. Information We Collect</h2>
            <p>We may collect and process the following data about you:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li><strong>Contact Information:</strong> Name, professional email address, and phone number.</li>
              <li><strong>Business Details:</strong> Company name, registration number, and VAT details.</li>
              <li><strong>Technical Data:</strong> IP address, browser type, and usage statistics via cookies to improve website performance.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <!-- Section 3 -->
          <section class="space-y-4">
            <h2 class="text-white text-2xl font-serif">3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
            <p>We use the information held about you in the following ways:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>To provide wholesale quotes and fulfill trade inquiries.</li>
              <li>To manage logistics and delivery of wholesale goods to your business.</li>
              <li>To comply with legal and tax obligations in the United Kingdom.</li>
              <li>To maintain our internal business records.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <!-- Section 4 -->
          <section class="space-y-4">
            <h2 class="text-white text-2xl font-serif">4. Data Retention</h2>
            <p>
              We will only retain your personal data for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes we collected it for, including for the purposes of satisfying any legal, accounting, or reporting requirements. Typically, trade inquiry data is held for up to 6 years in accordance with UK tax laws.
            </p>
          </section>

          <!-- Section 5 -->
          <section class="space-y-4 border-l border-[#D4AF37]/30 pl-8 bg-white/5 p-8">
            <h2 class="text-white text-2xl font-serif">5. Your Legal Rights</h2>
            <p>Under the UK GDPR, you have the following rights:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 italic">
              <li>The right to access your personal data.</li>
              <li>The right to request correction of inaccurate data.</li>
              <li>The right to request erasure of your data ("right to be forgotten").</li>
              <li>The right to object to processing or request restriction of processing.</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-4">To exercise these rights, please contact us at the address provided below.</p>
          </section>

          <!-- Section 6 -->
          <section class="space-y-4">
            <h2 class="text-white text-2xl font-serif">6. Contact & Data Protection</h2>
            <p>For any questions regarding this policy or our privacy practices, please contact our head office:</p>
            <div class="bg-black/40 p-8 border border-white/5 space-y-2 text-sm">
              <p class="text-white font-bold">BINGOPLACE LIMITED</p>
              <p>Attn: Data Protection Officer</p>
              <p>76 King Street</p>
              <p>Manchester, England</p>
              <p>M2 4NH</p>
              <p class="text-[#D4AF37] mt-4">Email: privacy@bingoplaceltd.com</p>
            </div>
          </section>

        </div>

        <div class="mt-20 pt-10 border-t border-white/5">
          <a href="/" class="text-[#D4AF37] uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px] font-bold hover:text-white transition-colors flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18"/></svg>
            Back to Home
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Ensure the serif font is applied to headers within the prose */
  h1, h2, h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  }
</style>